  "title": "Night Shift Bakers",
  "description": "<p><strong>Night Shift Central Kitchen Bakers</strong></p><p>No experience? Experienced baker? <strong>We want you!</strong><br /><br />Something <strong>exciting is baking</strong> at Tiong Bahru Bakery — a brand-new concept with fresh products is on the way, and we need <strong>MORE</strong> <strong>passionate, energetic bakers</strong> to bring it all to life in our growing team at the Central Kitchen.</p><p>Whether you’re just starting out or have mastered the art of bread, there’s a place for you in our team. And don’t worry about the early hours — your <strong>transport is reimbursed</strong> for the midnight shift! 🚕</p><h3><strong>What You’ll Do</strong></h3><ul><li><p>🥖 <strong>Craft Signature Breads & New Creations</strong> – shape, bake, and perfect breads that will delight Singapore</p></li><li><p>👩‍🍳 <strong>Learn or Share Your Skills</strong> – beginners get hands-on training, experienced bakers bring their expertise to the team</p></li><li><p>⚡ <strong>Work in a Buzzing Kitchen</strong> – at the heart of our exciting new launch</p></li><li><p>🌟 <strong>Make an Impact</strong> – help bring fresh, innovative breads to life across our outlets</p></li></ul><h3><strong>What We’re Looking For</strong></h3><ul><li><p>Commitment to the <strong>perform midnight shift</strong> (transport covered!)</p></li><li><p>Reliable, positive, and a <strong>true team player</strong></p></li><li><p>Passion for baking — whether you’re just starting out or already experienced</p></li><li><p>Eagerness to <strong>learn, grow, and innovate</strong> in a collaborative environment</p></li></ul><h3><strong>Perks & Benefits</strong></h3><ul><li><p>🎓 <strong>Training Provided</strong> – for beginners and skill refreshers</p></li><li><p>🍽️ <strong>Meal & Transport Allowance</strong></p></li><li><p>🌙 <strong>Night Shift Allowance</strong></p></li><li><p>🌿 <strong>Group Employee Benefits</strong></p></li><li><p>✨ The pride of saying: “I helped launch that!”</p></li></ul>",
